Rating: 2
This was just OK. I used fresh grated ginger instead of crystallized. I actually added the sugar and lime last, and I think it tasted better with just lime zest added. The sugar and lime seemed to mute and blend all the other flavors, making it sort of bland. This was definitely a case where the combined ingredients were less tasty than the individual ingredients. Not impressed.

